{"sentences":[{"w":"您","zh":"您是我们的老师吗？","py":"Nín shì wǒmen de lǎoshī ma?","en":"Are you our teacher?"},{"w":"您","zh":"您有几个朋友？","py":"Nín yǒu jǐ gè péngyǒu?","en":"How many friends do you have?"},{"w":"它","zh":"它是我的猫。","py":"Tā shì wǒ de māo.","en":"It is my cat."},{"w":"它","zh":"它喜欢吃米饭吗？","py":"Tā xǐhuan chī mǐfàn ma?","en":"Does it like to eat rice?"},{"w":"大家","zh":"大家好，我是老师。","py":"Dàjiā hǎo, wǒ shì lǎoshī.","en":"Hello everyone, I am a teacher."},{"w":"大家","zh":"大家都在这儿吗？","py":"Dàjiā dōu zài zhèr ma?","en":"Is everyone here?"},{"w":"每","zh":"每个人都来了。","py":"Měi gè rén dōu lái le.","en":"Everyone has come."},{"w":"每","zh":"我每天都学习汉语。","py":"Wǒ měi tiān dōu xuéxí Hànyǔ.","en":"I study Chinese every day."},{"w":"为什么","zh":"你为什么在这里？","py":"Nǐ wèishénme zài zhèlǐ?","en":"Why are you here?"},{"w":"为什么","zh":"他为什么不来？","py":"Tā wèishénme bù lái?","en":"Why does he not come?"},{"w":"零","zh":"这个字是零吗？","py":"Zhè gè zì shì líng ma?","en":"Is this character zero?"},{"w":"零","zh":"我没有零块钱。","py":"Wǒ méiyǒu líng kuài qián.","en":"I have no small change (zero money)."},{"w":"两","zh":"我有两本书。","py":"Wǒ yǒu liǎng běn shū.","en":"I have two books."},{"w":"两","zh":"他要两杯水。","py":"Tā yào liǎng bēi shuǐ.","en":"He wants two cups of water."},{"w":"百","zh":"我有一百块钱。","py":"Wǒ yǒu yì bǎi kuài qián.","en":"I have one hundred yuan."},{"w":"百","zh":"这个东西要一百吗？","py":"Zhè gè dōngxi yào yì bǎi ma?","en":"Does this thing cost one hundred?"},{"w":"千","zh":"他有一千块钱吗？","py":"Tā yǒu yì qiān kuài qián ma?","en":"Does he have one thousand yuan?"},{"w":"千","zh":"我想买一千个苹果。","py":"Wǒ xiǎng mǎi yì qiān gè píngguǒ.","en":"I want to buy one thousand apples."},{"w":"第一","zh":"这是我的第一本书。","py":"Zhè shì wǒ de dìyī běn shū.","en":"This is my first book."},{"w":"第一","zh":"他是我的第一位朋友。","py":"Tā shì wǒ de dìyī wèi péngyǒu.","en":"He is my first friend."},{"w":"次","zh":"这是我第一次来这里。","py":"Zhè shì wǒ dì yī cì lái zhèlǐ.","en":"This is my first time coming here."},{"w":"次","zh":"我想再去一次。","py":"Wǒ xiǎng zài qù yí cì.","en":"I want to go one more time."},{"w":"件","zh":"我买了一件衣服。","py":"Wǒ mǎi le yí jiàn yīfu.","en":"I bought one piece of clothing."},{"w":"件","zh":"这件东西是谁的？","py":"Zhè jiàn dōngxi shì shéi de?","en":"Whose item is this?"},{"w":"别","zh":"别说话。","py":"Bié shuōhuà.","en":"Do not speak."},{"w":"别","zh":"别吃那个。","py":"Bié chī nà gè.","en":"Do not eat that."},{"w":"非常","zh":"我非常喜欢苹果。","py":"Wǒ fēicháng xǐhuan píngguǒ.","en":"I really like apples."},{"w":"非常","zh":"他非常大。","py":"Tā fēicháng dà.","en":"He is extremely big."},{"w":"也","zh":"我也有一本书。","py":"Wǒ yě yǒu yì běn shū.","en":"I also have a book."},{"w":"也","zh":"她也在学汉语。","py":"Tā yě zài xué Hànyǔ.","en":"She is also learning Chinese."},{"w":"还","zh":"我还在学校。","py":"Wǒ hái zài xuéxiào.","en":"I am still at school."},{"w":"还","zh":"他还没来。","py":"Tā hái méi lái.","en":"He still hasn't come."},{"w":"最","zh":"我最喜欢喝茶。","py":"Wǒ zuì xǐhuan hē chá.","en":"I like drinking tea the most."},{"w":"最","zh":"她是我最好的朋友。","py":"Tā shì wǒ zuì hǎo de péngyǒu.","en":"She is my best friend."},{"w":"真","zh":"这个苹果真大。","py":"Zhè gè píngguǒ zhēn dà.","en":"This apple is really big."},{"w":"真","zh":"你真好。","py":"Nǐ zhēn hǎo.","en":"You are really nice."},{"w":"正在","zh":"我正在看书。","py":"Wǒ zhèngzài kàn shū.","en":"I am reading a book right now."},{"w":"正在","zh":"她正在吃饭。","py":"Tā zhèngzài chī fàn.","en":"She is eating right now."},{"w":"已经","zh":"我已经来了。","py":"Wǒ yǐjīng lái le.","en":"I have already arrived."},{"w":"已经","zh":"他们已经走了。","py":"Tāmen yǐjīng zǒu le.","en":"They have already left."},{"w":"一起","zh":"我们一起去吃饭吧。","py":"Wǒmen yìqǐ qù chī fàn ba.","en":"Let's go eat together."},{"w":"一起","zh":"你想和我一起看电影吗？","py":"Nǐ xiǎng hé wǒ yìqǐ kàn diànyǐng ma?","en":"Do you want to watch a movie together with me?"},{"w":"再","zh":"请再说一次。","py":"Qǐng zài shuō yí cì.","en":"Please say it again."},{"w":"再","zh":"我想再见他。","py":"Wǒ xiǎng zàijiàn tā.","en":"I want to see him again."},{"w":"就","zh":"我现在就去。","py":"Wǒ xiànzài jiù qù.","en":"I will go right now."},{"w":"就","zh":"他吃了就睡觉。","py":"Tā chī le jiù shuìjiào.","en":"He sleeps as soon as he finishes eating."},{"w":"因为……所以……","zh":"因为我累，所以我不去。","py":"Yīnwèi wǒ lèi, suǒyǐ wǒ bù qù.","en":"Because I am tired, so I will not go."},{"w":"因为……所以……","zh":"因为下雨，所以我在家。","py":"Yīnwèi xiàyǔ, suǒyǐ wǒ zài jiā.","en":"Because it is raining, so I am at home."},{"w":"虽然……但是……","zh":"虽然我累，但是我学习。","py":"Suīrán wǒ lèi, dànshì wǒ xuéxí.","en":"Although I am tired, I still study."},{"w":"虽然……但是……","zh":"虽然他很大，但是他很可爱。","py":"Suīrán tā hěn dà, dànshì tā hěn kě'ài.","en":"Although he is big, he is very cute."},{"w":"从","zh":"我从家去学校。","py":"Wǒ cóng jiā qù xuéxiào.","en":"I go to school from home."},{"w":"从","zh":"他从北京来了吗？","py":"Tā cóng Běijīng lái le ma?","en":"Did he come from Beijing?"},{"w":"比","zh":"我比你大。","py":"Wǒ bǐ nǐ dà.","en":"I am older than you."},{"w":"比","zh":"今天比昨天热。","py":"Jīntiān bǐ zuótiān rè.","en":"Today is hotter than yesterday."},{"w":"往","zh":"我往前面走。","py":"Wǒ wǎng qiánmiàn zǒu.","en":"I walk toward the front."},{"w":"往","zh":"请往左边看。","py":"Qǐng wǎng zuǒbiān kàn.","en":"Please look to the left."},{"w":"离","zh":"我家离学校很近吗？","py":"Wǒ jiā lí xuéxiào hěn jìn ma?","en":"Is my home close to the school?"},{"w":"离","zh":"这里离北京远吗？","py":"Zhèlǐ lí Běijīng yuǎn ma?","en":"Is it far from here to Beijing?"},{"w":"得","zh":"你说得很好。","py":"Nǐ shuō de hěn hǎo.","en":"You speak very well."},{"w":"得","zh":"他跑得很快。","py":"Tā pǎo de hěn kuài.","en":"He runs very fast."},{"w":"着","zh":"他看着书。","py":"Tā kàn zhe shū.","en":"He is reading the book (in a continuous state)."},{"w":"着","zh":"她笑着说你好。","py":"Tā xiào zhe shuō nǐ hǎo.","en":"She smiles while saying hello to you."},{"w":"过","zh":"我来过这里。","py":"Wǒ lái guò zhèlǐ.","en":"I have been here before."},{"w":"过","zh":"你吃过苹果吗？","py":"Nǐ chī guò píngguǒ ma?","en":"Have you eaten apples before?"},{"w":"吧","zh":"我们走吧。","py":"Wǒmen zǒu ba.","en":"Let's go."},{"w":"吧","zh":"你喝茶吧。","py":"Nǐ hē chá ba.","en":"You can have some tea."},{"w":"机场","zh":"我明天去机场。","py":"Wǒ míngtiān qù jīchǎng.","en":"I will go to the airport tomorrow."},{"w":"机场","zh":"北京有一个大机场吗？","py":"Běijīng yǒu yí gè dà jīchǎng ma?","en":"Does Beijing have a big airport?"},{"w":"教室","zh":"我们在教室学习。","py":"Wǒmen zài jiàoshì xuéxí.","en":"We study in the classroom."},{"w":"教室","zh":"那个教室很大。","py":"Nà gè jiàoshì hěn dà.","en":"That classroom is very big."},{"w":"房间","zh":"我住在那个房间。","py":"Wǒ zhù zài nà gè fángjiān.","en":"I live in that room."},{"w":"房间","zh":"这个房间很小。","py":"Zhè gè fángjiān hěn xiǎo.","en":"This room is very small."},{"w":"路","zh":"这条路很长吗？","py":"Zhè tiáo lù hěn cháng ma?","en":"Is this road very long?"},{"w":"路","zh":"我不认识这条路。","py":"Wǒ bù rènshi zhè tiáo lù.","en":"I don’t know this road."},{"w":"左边","zh":"猫在桌子左边。","py":"Māo zài zhuōzi zuǒbiān.","en":"The cat is on the left side of the table."},{"w":"左边","zh":"我家左边是商店。","py":"Wǒ jiā zuǒbiān shì shāngdiàn.","en":"On the left side of my house is a shop."},{"w":"右边","zh":"学校右边是饭店。","py":"Xuéxiào yòubiān shì fàndiàn.","en":"To the right of the school is a restaurant."},{"w":"右边","zh":"我坐在你右边。","py":"Wǒ zuò zài nǐ yòubiān.","en":"I sit on your right side."},{"w":"外","zh":"她在外面吗？","py":"Tā zài wàimiàn ma?","en":"Is she outside?"},{"w":"外","zh":"我不想去外面。","py":"Wǒ bù xiǎng qù wàimiàn.","en":"I don't want to go outside."},{"w":"旁边","zh":"我坐在你旁边。","py":"Wǒ zuò zài nǐ pángbiān.","en":"I sit next to you."},{"w":"旁边","zh":"教室旁边是厕所吗？","py":"Jiàoshì pángbiān shì cèsuǒ ma?","en":"Is there a restroom next to the classroom?"},{"w":"一下","zh":"请等一下。","py":"Qǐng děng yíxià.","en":"Please wait a moment."},{"w":"一下","zh":"你看一下这个。","py":"Nǐ kàn yíxià zhè gè.","en":"Take a quick look at this."},{"w":"早上","zh":"我早上去学校。","py":"Wǒ zǎoshàng qù xuéxiào.","en":"I go to school in the morning."},{"w":"早上","zh":"早上好，你吃了吗？","py":"Zǎoshàng hǎo, nǐ chī le ma?","en":"Good morning, did you eat?"},{"w":"晚上","zh":"我晚上看电视。","py":"Wǒ wǎnshàng kàn diànshì.","en":"I watch TV at night."},{"w":"晚上","zh":"他晚上很忙。","py":"Tā wǎnshàng hěn máng.","en":"He is busy at night."},{"w":"小时","zh":"我等了一个小时。","py":"Wǒ děng le yí gè xiǎoshí.","en":"I waited for one hour."},{"w":"小时","zh":"你只有两小时吗？","py":"Nǐ zhǐ yǒu liǎng xiǎoshí ma?","en":"Do you only have two hours?"},{"w":"时间","zh":"我没有时间。","py":"Wǒ méiyǒu shíjiān.","en":"I don't have time."},{"w":"时间","zh":"你有时间帮我吗？","py":"Nǐ yǒu shíjiān bāng wǒ ma?","en":"Do you have time to help me?"},{"w":"去年","zh":"我去年在北京。","py":"Wǒ qùnián zài Běijīng.","en":"I was in Beijing last year."},{"w":"去年","zh":"去年他是学生。","py":"Qùnián tā shì xuéshēng.","en":"He was a student last year."},{"w":"日","zh":"今天是五月五日。","py":"Jīntiān shì wǔ yuè wǔ rì.","en":"Today is May 5th."},{"w":"日","zh":"他生日是哪日？","py":"Tā shēngrì shì nǎ rì?","en":"Which date is his birthday?"},{"w":"生日","zh":"我的生日在五月。","py":"Wǒ de shēngrì zài wǔ yuè.","en":"My birthday is in May."},{"w":"生日","zh":"你生日想做什么？","py":"Nǐ shēngrì xiǎng zuò shénme?","en":"What do you want to do on your birthday?"},{"w":"哥哥","zh":"我哥哥是医生。","py":"Wǒ gēge shì yīshēng.","en":"My older brother is a doctor."},{"w":"哥哥","zh":"哥哥喜欢看电影。","py":"Gēge xǐhuan kàn diànyǐng.","en":"Older brother likes watching movies."},{"w":"姐姐","zh":"姐姐在商店工作。","py":"Jiějie zài shāngdiàn gōngzuò.","en":"My older sister works in a shop."},{"w":"姐姐","zh":"我姐姐很漂亮。","py":"Wǒ jiějie hěn piàoliang.","en":"My older sister is very beautiful."},{"w":"弟弟","zh":"弟弟喜欢玩。","py":"Dìdi xǐhuan wán.","en":"Younger brother likes to play."},{"w":"弟弟","zh":"我弟弟在看电视。","py":"Wǒ dìdi zài kàn diànshì.","en":"My younger brother is watching TV."},{"w":"妹妹","zh":"妹妹是学生。","py":"Mèimei shì xuéshēng.","en":"My younger sister is a student."},{"w":"妹妹","zh":"她妹妹很可爱。","py":"Tā mèimei hěn kě'ài.","en":"Her younger sister is very cute."},{"w":"丈夫","zh":"我丈夫在家吗？","py":"Wǒ zhàngfu zài jiā ma?","en":"Is my husband at home?"},{"w":"丈夫","zh":"她的丈夫是医生。","py":"Tā de zhàngfu shì yīshēng.","en":"Her husband is a doctor."},{"w":"妻子","zh":"他妻子不在家。","py":"Tā qīzi bú zài jiā.","en":"His wife is not at home."},{"w":"妻子","zh":"你的妻子在工作吗？","py":"Nǐ de qīzi zài gōngzuò ma?","en":"Is your wife working?"},{"w":"孩子","zh":"她有一个孩子。","py":"Tā yǒu yí gè háizi.","en":"She has one child."},{"w":"孩子","zh":"孩子在看书。","py":"Háizi zài kàn shū.","en":"The child is reading."},{"w":"男人","zh":"那个男人是谁？","py":"Nà gè nánrén shì shéi?","en":"Who is that man?"},{"w":"男人","zh":"男人在吃饭。","py":"Nánrén zài chī fàn.","en":"The man is eating."},{"w":"女人","zh":"那个女人很漂亮。","py":"Nà gè nǚrén hěn piàoliang.","en":"That woman is very beautiful."},{"w":"女人","zh":"女人在打电话。","py":"Nǚrén zài dǎ diànhuà.","en":"The woman is making a phone call."},{"w":"服务员","zh":"服务员，你好！","py":"Fúwùyuán, nǐ hǎo!","en":"Hello, waiter!"},{"w":"服务员","zh":"请叫服务员来。","py":"Qǐng jiào fúwùyuán lái.","en":"Please call the waiter over."},{"w":"鱼","zh":"我喜欢吃鱼。","py":"Wǒ xǐhuan chī yú.","en":"I like to eat fish."},{"w":"鱼","zh":"这条鱼很好吃。","py":"Zhè tiáo yú hěn hǎo chī.","en":"This fish is delicious."},{"w":"羊肉","zh":"你喜欢吃羊肉吗？","py":"Nǐ xǐhuan chī yángròu ma?","en":"Do you like to eat mutton?"},{"w":"羊肉","zh":"我没有羊肉。","py":"Wǒ méiyǒu yángròu.","en":"I don't have mutton."},{"w":"牛奶","zh":"我想喝牛奶。","py":"Wǒ xiǎng hē niúnǎi.","en":"I want to drink milk."},{"w":"牛奶","zh":"他没有牛奶了。","py":"Tā méiyǒu niúnǎi le.","en":"He has no milk left."},{"w":"鸡蛋","zh":"我每天吃鸡蛋。","py":"Wǒ měitiān chī jīdàn.","en":"I eat eggs every day."},{"w":"鸡蛋","zh":"你想要几个鸡蛋？","py":"Nǐ xiǎng yào jǐ gè jīdàn?","en":"How many eggs do you want?"},{"w":"西瓜","zh":"这个西瓜很甜吗？","py":"Zhè gè xīguā hěn tián ma?","en":"Is this watermelon very sweet?"},{"w":"西瓜","zh":"我想买一个西瓜。","py":"Wǒ xiǎng mǎi yí gè xīguā.","en":"I want to buy a watermelon."},{"w":"咖啡","zh":"我喜欢喝咖啡。","py":"Wǒ xǐhuan hē kāfēi.","en":"I like drinking coffee."},{"w":"咖啡","zh":"你想喝咖啡吗？","py":"Nǐ xiǎng hē kāfēi ma?","en":"Do you want to drink coffee?"},{"w":"雪","zh":"今天下雪吗？","py":"Jīntiān xià xuě ma?","en":"Is it snowing today?"},{"w":"雪","zh":"我喜欢看雪。","py":"Wǒ xǐhuan kàn xuě.","en":"I like watching snow."},{"w":"药","zh":"我买了药。","py":"Wǒ mǎi le yào.","en":